-- hub's approach -- full copy of the old feature-rich version kept in
-- UE_Legacy_Full.lua. This loads standalone (Serenity no longer exposes a shared
-- runtime/theme table for modules to hook into). Base TP and Full Bright are wired up.
-- Auto Farm runs the old hub's "Auto Trap" logic verbatim (Hunter Trap / Graveyard /
-- Ancient Ruins detection, fight the wave, collect drops, open key-gated crates,
-- auto-sell, self-defense, idle crate sweep) -- only the ESP/HubState/keybind/rarity-
-- filter plumbing around it was dropped since this panel doesn't have that shared UI.
-- ESP itself is still just laid out, not wired up.
