-- feature (UE_Legacy_Full.lua). Detects Hunter Trap / Graveyard / Ancient Ruins
-- structures as they spawn, teleports to trigger them, fights the enemy wave, claims
-- ground drops, opens any key-gated loot crate, returns to base, and repeats. Sweeps
-- leftover crates when idle, auto-sells the backpack once it fills up, and fights back
-- against anything that gets close while farming.
--
-- The only things dropped from the original are the pieces that depended on the old
-- hub's shared HubState/ThemeObjects/keybind/rarity-filter-dock plumbing, which this
-- standalone panel doesn't have: pickup rarity filtering now always allows every drop
-- (matching the old default of every rarity being enabled), and there's no keybind or
-- ESP-alert wiring. The actual farming state machine below is unchanged.
-- ============================================================================
